":func:`TSHttpHdrStatusGet`, which retrieves the status code from an HTTP "
"response header (:func:`TSHttpHdrStatusGet` retrieves status codes only "
"from headers of type :data:`TS_HTTP_TYPE_RESPONSE`)."
msgstr ""

# 1aef54ca3a21488798521aebf1ce8461
#: ../../developer-guide/api/functions/TSTypes.en.rst:89
